OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG2018F50th anniversary edition of BBC
OL,7,FLook North airs on BBC One Yorkshire.
OL,8,
OL,9,FPresented by Harry Gration and Amy
OL,10,FGarcia, with Paul Hudson (weather).
OL,11,FMany former colleagues appeared,
OL,12,Fincluding Sophie Raworth, Philip Hayton
OL,13,Fand Tim Ewart.
OL,14,
OL,15,FThe programme was broadcast live from
OL,16,FOld Broadcasting House, Woodhouse Lane,
OL,17,Fwhere it was based from 1974 until
OL,18,F2004.
